## Debug Tools

### Debug Toggles (When Applicable)

For visual/interactive projects, implement these keyboard shortcuts:

```javascript
// Debug system toggles
D - Toggle debug mode
G - Toggle grid/layout visualization
B - Toggle bounding boxes
C - Toggle collision visualization
P - Toggle performance metrics
L - Toggle logging
H - Toggle help overlay (show all debug keys)
```

### Implementation Template

```javascript
class DebugManager {
  constructor() {
    this.enabled = false;
    this.showGrid = false;
    this.showBounds = false;
    this.showCollisions = false;
    this.showPerformance = false;
    
    this.setupKeyboardShortcuts();
  }
  
  setupKeyboardShortcuts() {
    window.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
      switch(e.key.toLowerCase()) {
        case 'd': this.enabled = !this.enabled; break;
        case 'g': this.showGrid = !this.showGrid; break;
        case 'b': this.showBounds = !this.showBounds; break;
        case 'c': this.showCollisions = !this.showCollisions; break;
        case 'p': this.showPerformance = !this.showPerformance; break;
        case 'h': this.showHelp(); break;
      }
    });
  }
  
  render(ctx) {
    if (!this.enabled) return;
    
    if (this.showGrid) this.renderGrid(ctx);
    if (this.showBounds) this.renderBounds(ctx);
    if (this.showCollisions) this.renderCollisions(ctx);
    if (this.showPerformance) this.renderPerformance(ctx);
  }
}
```

### Console Logging

**Development mode**:
```javascript
class Logger {
  static debug(message, data) {
    if (CONFIG.DEBUG_MODE) {
      console.log(`[DEBUG] ${message}`, data);
    }
  }
  
  static warn(message, data) {
    console.warn(`[WARN] ${message}`, data);
  }
  
  static error(message, data) {
    console.error(`[ERROR] ${message}`, data);
  }
}

// Usage
Logger.debug('Entity spawned', { id: entity.id, pos: entity.position });
```

